============
Project info
============

Author: Kosei Kitahara <surgo.jp@gmail.com>
Project host: http://bitbucket.org/Surgo/rtm.vim/

=====
Usage
=====

Add Task
--------

 * add current line to task
   `:C[RTM] -a` command
 * add current buffer to task
   `:B[RTM] -a` command

